  @{"°"} @{"  Coders & Origins  "} @{"°°"} @{"°"}

  Every effort has been made by myself to include as many MAXs Door Coders
  and anyone else who has contributed to MAXs itself in this list. If your
  name is missing and you wish your name to be in the list,  then read the
  @{" information " link info} section. Using my huge MAXs collection (the largest in the
  southern hemisphere, if not the world),  I searched through all the docs
  of doors and archives to put the below list together.   This list is not
  a complete list, as MAXs contributors have come and gone. No-one knows?!

  Apart from the  Australian contributors being listed first,  the list is
  in no particular order, whether the coders names be true or not.  I have
  used full names only, except where the real name is not known,  an alias
  is used, but only in this listing.

