  @{"°"} @{"  Greets & Credits  "} @{"°°"} @{"°"}


  The idea and creation of this guide came about by me being bored, and so
  I had to do something, thus "MAXs Door Coders" guide was born.. Wow?! :)
  This guide may or may not be useful.. So what, it's been done, so be it!
  I have created this guide in support of MAXs, but also really to have it 
  dedicated to everyone who has used and/or still uses the MAXs software!

  This guide may not be altered in any way except by Glen Martin (Marty)!!


  Hello to @{b}Zeffy@{ub}, Steve Clack, Niki Murkett, Mathew Emerson, Olly and Erik
