  ----------------------
   @{b}Coder's Door Listing@{ub}
  ======================


  The following list is always updated and current as of 01-Dec-98.
  It show everything I've done as a MAXs Door Coder, most of my work.

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Door/package              Description
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------

   AFL_TiPS.lha              AFL sport tipping competition
   AmiVote.lha               Voting poll on questions
   AmiWall.lha               Small grafitti wall
   BBS-Advert.lha            Displays up to 10 adverts
   CallBBS.lha               Add to and display BBS list
   FFL_14.lha                Allows a fast login for SysOp/users v1.4
   FFL_v13.lha               Allows a fast login for SysOp/users
   FLE-A-CDRoM.lzx           Adult version CD-rom door for FLE
   FLE-CDRoM.lha             CD-rom door for FLE SysOps
   fLE-sTATS.lha             Screen showing stats for FLE
   FLE_096.lha               File Lister Express v.096
   FLE_GoodBye.lha           Logoff and checks for marked files
   fle_secname.lha           Shows FLE file section
   FLE_TOPs.lha              Top FLE uploader and downloaders
   FLE_UTiL.lha              FLE user listing util
   Fluffy_Guide.lha          Guide on BBS's in Fluffy Net
   FOR_SALE_21.lha           Add/read for sale & wanted adverts
   FUKWiTS_21.lha            Keep unwanted users off BBS
   Fukwits_22.lha            Keep unwanted users off BBS v2.2
   Glen_Martin.lha           Iff picture of Glen Martin
   HangAmi.lha               Hamgman guess words game
   HD_Menus.lha              Set of menus for Hackers Delight
   IntroStats.lha            Screen for displaying data
   IS_22.lha                 Screen for displaying data v2.2
   LAST10.lha                Displays last 10 callers
   Log_User.lha              Logs user when they log in
   MAXsTD.lha                Run MAXs and Trapdoor together
   MAXs_Coders.lha           Past and Present MAXs People
   MAXs_Files.lha            Gremlins BBS MAXs file listings
   MAXs_Guide.lha            MAXs documentation in guide format
   MiSSiON.lha               A text game for Multidoor
   MMC_Pack.lha              Mega Multinode ansi pack
   Multi-Menus.lha           Allows several menus on a BBS v1.2
   Multi_Menus.lha           Allows several menus on a BBS
   My_Version.rego           Gremlins My Version rego form
   NBL-TiPS.lha              NBL sport tipping competition
   nEW_uSER.lha              Log-in sequence for a BBS
   New_User_v2.lha           Log-in sequence for a BBS v2.0
   No_Password.lha           For users with forgotton passwords
   oBBS_LiST_35.lha          BBS listings for Australia BBS's
   PaPa_Pack1.lha            Various offsets for MAXs PRO BBS
   PASSW_CHECK.lha           Ask user to change password
   PW_Check.lha              Ask user to change password v1.1
   Read_Me_2.lha             Displays BBS info texts
   SETTiNGS.lha              Change MAXs settings with a heading
   Setup_10.lha              User settings with a difference
   Show_Grems!.lha           10 min ansi preview of Gremlins BBS
   Slow_User.lha             Displays a screen to slow modem users
   Speed_11.lha              Allows a fast login for users
   Stufff.lha                Lotsa stuff related to Gremlins BBS
   SUPER_LOG.lha             Shows last 10 callers and stats
   SysOpMenu.lha             SysOp only functions in a menu
   SYSTEM_STATS.lha          Shows all your computer details
   S_Log12_NSA.lha           Shows last 10 callers and stats v.NSA
   The_Wall_11.lha           Another grafitti wall
   The_Wall_12.lha           Another grafitti wall v1.2
   Time_Bank.lha             MAXs time bank options in menu
   U2S.lha                   Upload 2 SysOp type door
   Upload2SysOp.lha          Allows uploads direct to SysOp
   US_FLE.lha                FLE user stats screen
   UserMsg.lha               Add/display last user message
   Users_List.lha            Shows listings of all users info
   User_Cfg.lha              Change MAXs settings in menu
   USER_CHECK.lha            Checks up on users and their details
   USER_MSG_32.lha           Excellent add/display user msg
   USER_MSG_35.lha           Excellent add/display user msg v3.5

  ------------------------------------------------------------------------

  That's pretty much my complete list of MAXs stuff. Some doors were also
  joint created, mainly the FLE doors. And yeah, more MAXs stuff soon! :)

